parameters: \nc<Saki>Phew... somehow managed to get through this term as well.
\bustMoveHome[2, 30]\nc<Senpai>Saki, have you finished the work I asked for last week?
\bustMsgExpression[1, 0]\nc<Saki>Ah, just a moment please. Um, that...\bustMsgExpression[1,1]...huh?

\nc<Saki>The computer won't turn on. This is bad, the last backup was
a month ago...
\nc<Senpai>So, what about the task I requested?

\nc<Saki>Just, just a second please! That...\bustMsgExp[1, 0] Ah,
it's powered on.

\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>What is this?! If you want to recover the files, send
Meatcoin... what?

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>Oh, not again? It happens from time to time. The internal
network has almost no security, so it gets hacked like this.

\nc<Senpai>There's no choice but to give up. Do you think the company
will pay to recover the files?
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>No way... Isn't there anything we can do?!

\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>You said the last backup was a month ago, right? It would be
faster to recreate the documents than to learn hacking at
this point.

\nc<Senpai>Check if there's anything you sent to other teams. If you
ask them nicely, maybe they'll send it back to you.

\nc<Saki>Yes... Thank you very much. So, about the work I was asked
to do...

\nc<Senpai>I feel sorry for you, so I'll let it slide just this once.
Make sure to process and send what I asked for by the end of
work today.
\nc<Senpai>That's why I told you to send it as soon as you're done.
\nc<Saki>But Senpai, you get mad if I send it over the weekend...
\nc<Saki>Sigh... Do I have to start all over again...

\TA[1]We have achieved this term's conditions. Collecting magical
power now.
\TA[1]The target for the next term is 60,000 magical power.
